{{codepointer|Jump}}
state '''A_JumpIfTargetOutsideMeleeRange'''(int ''offset'')<br>
state '''A_JumpIfTargetOutsideMeleeRange'''(str ''state'')
{{JumpNotice}}
== Usage ==
Jumps the number of frames (''offset'') forward, or to the specified ''state'' when the target of the calling actor is beyond {{Property|MeleeRange|melee range}} of the caller.

